.register-hero
  .container
    .hero-text.col-md-6
      h1.header-light All your lessons and all your students. All in one place.
      p.subheader-light Welcome to TeacherTracker, an online platform for private lesson teachers
      btn.btn.btn-primary.main-btn.hero(href="#register-box") Get Started Now
.register-background
  .container
    .register-exp.col-md-7
      .text-section
        h2 The Easy Way to Teach Lessons
        p Ever had a student walk and you can't remember who they are or what they're working on? Those embarrassing days are over! Lesson Portal is a simple, on-line solution for private lesson teachers. Keep track of students and lesson plans all in one place.
        h4.bullet <i class="fa fa-calendar-o"></i> Schedule With Ease
        h4.bullet <i class="fa fa-file-text-o"></i> Maintain Lesson Plans
        h4.bullet <i class="fa fa-check-square-o"></i> Track Student Progress
    div(id="register-box")
      .register-box.col-md-5
        h2 Register
        p Join TeacherTracker today!
        form(class="form" ng-submit="register.register()")
          .form-group
              input.form-control(type="text" name="username" placeholder="Enter Username" ng-model="register.info.username" required)
          .form-group
            input.form-control(type="password" name="password" placeholder="Password" ng-model="register.info.password" required)
          button.btn.btn-default.main-btn(type="submit") Submit
          a(href='/')
            button.btn.btn-primary.sec-btn(type="button") Cancel
          p.register-cta Already have an account?
            a.register-link(href="/#/login") Sign In Now


